==League Seasons==
[[Image:UBOLeague.jpg|left]]
Ultimate Baseball Online features seasonal leagues that feature multiple teams of different levels playing against each other for the championship. There are three league classes: Elite, All-Star, and Major. Leagues usually feature a 10-game regular season, 3 wildcard playoff games, 4 division final games, and a 5-game league championship. UBO Press Coverage and Awards are also presented during the league seasons. All winners of UBO 2007 Leagues earn an entry into the Best of UBO 2007.
